Jimicsiyada

Laga soo bilaabo 2008 ilaa 2010, tababarka iyo wareegga aqooneed ee AMANI AFRICA I (oo ah "nabadda Afrika," ee Swahili), loogu talagalay in lagu qiimeeyo waxtarka ASF ee howlgalka nabad ilaalinta nabadda ee Midowga Afrika (PSO) ay qabatay Midowga Afrika oo wada shaqeyn oo leh Midowga Yurub. Waxay u muuqataa in jimicsiga kowaad ee koonfureed loo yaqaan 'Command Post Exercise (CPX), noocan oo kale ah ee Addis Ababa. AMANI AFRICA Waxan xoogga saaraayey ansixinta siyaasadaha iyo geedi socodka, heerarka istaraatiijiga ee xuduudaha ah, ee loo shaqeynayo Ciidanka Afrikaanka ah ee Gargaarka ah ee ku yaala Bariga Afrika ee Nabadgalyada iyo Nabadgelyada (APSA). Sida laga soo xigtay Midowga Afrika, waxay bixisay caddayn ujeedo ah oo lagu taageerayo soo jeedinta ku aaddan horumarinta ururada iyo horumarinta hawlaha tababarka, nidaamyada iyo kartida ballaaran ee ASF.


 


